828 uint8_t sx1262_single_receive(sx1262_handle_t *handle, double us)

1269  ms--; /* ms-- */

1285  return 6; /* return error */
1286  }

1289  handle->debug_print("sx1262: unknown result.\n"); /* unknown result */
